{"tid":2256064,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人後悔過減肥","createTime":"2020-10-24T05:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T05:43:56.000Z","uid":121289,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f17657342f128e8f816110fe91e559954e05e560","tid":2256064,"uid":121289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T05:20:39.000Z","msg":"1米83<br />\n3個月前93kg BF 27%<br />\n宜家79kg BF 20.5%<br />\n講真本來我食量就唔算多 同同事朋友食飯份量都係差唔多咁 零食幾乎冇咁制<br />\n但為左減肥就多管齊下 戎碳唔食飯/麵/麵包 <br />\n又要斷食16個鐘所以跳左早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每日仲要抽個半鐘做gym 重訓有氧齊齊做 平日返工都做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感覺呢3個月個人好似坐緊監咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家諗諗下都唔知自己為咩 未減之前冇人話我肥 減左之後又冇人話我瘦左<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本來目標係75kg 17%BF 宜家諗住1個禮拜剩係做2-3次運動算<br />\n希望唔好反彈得咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n奉勸大家如果唔係肥得好撚誇張果D真係唔好搏老命減<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n健康地肥仲好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529fdb735cb125b0f142f749b62e1cc2ce332b16","tid":2256064,"uid":27996,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"183 93kg都唔算肥得誇張？<br />\n米9個啲大隻仔都冇咁重啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64db8ce296e3b954b3d742adcadbdb233ea75837","tid":2256064,"uid":88022,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T05:47:54.000Z","msg":"我185先80Kg<br />\n仲要肌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你93 好撚大隻"},{"pid":"3ec0c6355da2204c0eaf108166e4718f8bd7f204","tid":2256064,"uid":188374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T05:49:38.000Z","msg":"183 93kg bf27極肥喎 咁都唔誇張?<br />\n為咩?為健康 冇健康肥呢樣野 其次先係為身材"},{"pid":"e5125777c3a30856a922b34133995bb6466580b9","tid":2256064,"uid":3104,"like":0,"di